## 🛠️ Installation & Requirements

To install and set up XENO BRUTE on Kali Linux, follow these steps:

### 1. Requirements
Ensure you have the following installed:
- `tor`
- `python3` & `pip3`
- `lolcat`
- `wget`
- `git`

### 2. Clone & Setup
```bash
# Clone the official repository
git clone https://github.com/XENO-XD-V2/Insta-Brute-Force.git

# Enter the directory
cd Insta-Brute-Force

# Run the automated setup script
sudo bash setup.sh
```

### 3. Manual Installation Commands
If you prefer manual setup, run the following:

```bash
# Update System
sudo apt update && sudo apt upgrade -y

# Install Dependencies
sudo apt install tor python3 python3-pip wget lolcat git -y

# Install Python Modules
pip3 install requests requests[socks] stem instagram-py

# Configure Tor (Standard Path)
# Ensure your torrc is correctly configured in /etc/tor/torrc
```

